{"tid":2143753,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蘋果：香港核酸檢測公司Prenetics 的專家團隊其中一成員 表示沒有與該公司合作","createTime":"2020-08-07T09:24:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-07T12:41:18.000Z","uid":22556,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"14638066716dc9c41b0245345613e3cc88954a78","tid":2143753,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T09:24:42.000Z","msg":"全民免費檢測推出在即，政府欽點的3間核酸檢測公司卻接連被揭有問題，《蘋果》最新調查發現，為食肆員工提供檢測的Prenetics更涉挪用專家「光環」。Prenetics在網站聲稱核酸檢測計劃由「專業醫療團隊」領導，但團隊其中一名海外專家向《蘋果》表示，除了幾年前曾為Prenetics主講幾場講座，與對方根本再無合作和聯絡，對被列入團隊亦不知情。《蘋果》正就事件向Prenetics查詢。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200807/4NCB7R6JEGOLSCNEWNWEALNB5A/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200807%2F4NCB7R6JEGOLSCNEWNWEALNB5A%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=ACvVw7CXGjn4pyDVYlJlLIsqpp%2BZ5aV1zu33iQ7YiKA%3D&h=5d91873b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200807%2F4NCB7R6JEGOLSCNEWNWEALNB5A%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=47aef098\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200807/4NCB7R6JEGOLSCNEWNWEALNB5A/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"99852f093b9b9b983137054c603b3acbbc9301b0","tid":2143753,"uid":57532,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T09:26:26.000Z","msg":"一間就驗車, 一間就被列入團隊亦不知情, 跟本就係正苦迫人收錢."},{"pid":"5934f8a40f60254bd4cb61672d4fca4645378d08","tid":2143753,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T09:40:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img sr